Alright, so. Everyone apparently has different experiences with torrents like these. After about 3 hours of trying to download this here is what I have done:

1) Download torrent. 
2) Install Photoshop by running the setup file and following the setup instructions from Adobe. 
3) Launched Photoshop.
4) Received serial code error.

I expected this. Not a big deal really, so I went and downloaded a crack.

5) Downloaded https://thepiratebay.se/torrent/5570840/Adobe_Photoshop_CS5_Extended_(Crack___Instructions)
6) Followed the instructions INCLUDED in the crack download. 
7) Use all the serials INCLUDED in crack download.
8) Received different error, the "We are unable to start your subscription" error.

Adobe implemented a new antipirating thing. Found out that it has to do with serials.

9) Went back to http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/6664771/Adobe_Photoshop_CS5 and tried all the serials over again.

10) The very last serial worked, but not the first few and a couple in the middle. 

So yeah. Make sure you try all the serials, because that's what Adobe is aiming to stop. ALSO! Hosts files! Make sure you use cracks.
